    dc:creator "Bartsch, Daniel" ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic changes in Synanthedonini from Madagascar, with description of two new genera and species (Lepidoptera: Sesiidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1287075>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1287077> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1287075>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–12. Adult specimens of Madagascan Synanthedonini: 1–5. Rodolphia hombergi Le Cerf, 1911. (1–2) male, Madagascar, Bekily, Region sud de l’Ile. (4–5) female, same data. (3) male, holotype of Malgassesia pauliani Viette, 1955, ventral view. 6–7. Malgassesia andrianony (Viette, 1982) comb. nov., male holotype. 8–12. Malgassesia rufescens Le Cerf, 1922. (8–9) male, Madagascar, Ihosy, Region sud de l’Ile. (10–11) female, Madagascar, Bekily, Region sud de l’Ile. (12) female, holotype of Malgassesia biedermanni Viette, 1982. Scale bars 10 mm, ventral view right." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1287075/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1287077>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–24. Adult specimens of Madagascan Synanthedonini: 13–14. Malgassesia lemur (Le Cerf, 1957) comb. nov., male holotype. 15–16. Malgassesia ferdinandi nom. nov., male holotype. 17–19. Epitarsipus rufithorax Le Cerf, 1922 comb. rev. (17–18) male, Madagascar, Bekily, Region sud de l’Ile. (19) female, same data. 20–22. Cinctosesia polistiformis sp. nov. (20–21) male holotype (freshly emerged specimen). (22) male paratype (older specimen). 23–24. Nesosphecia mystica sp. nov., male holotype. Scale bars 10 mm, ventral view right." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1287077/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

